-- Shiny Secure — composition example.
-- Extends shiny with security-audit aspect.
-- This is Cell's answer to TOML's extends + compose.

## shiny-secure

  import shiny
  import security-audit

  -- Apply security scans around implement and submit steps
  apply security-audit(implement, submit)

  -- All cells from shiny are inherited.
  -- security-audit recipe adds prescan/postscan around implement and submit.
  -- No other changes needed. The molecule is shiny + security gates.

